<lyrics>[V1]
 1- sirũ ạltũqay̱ siruⁿ̃ ʿaẓīm̊
 ạllhu bāna fī ạl̊jasad̊
 barãrahu ạlrũwḥu ạl̊ḥakīm̊
 waqad̊ tarāʾay̱ waṣaʿid̊

[V2]
 2- kulã kẖaṭāyānā ḥamal̊
 fī jis̊mihi ʿalay̱ ạlṣãlīb̊
 daẙnūnaẗaⁿ kadẖā ạḥ̊tamal̊
 waqad̊ wafay̱ ạldãẙna ạlrãhīb̊

[V3]
 3- jāzat̊ ʿalaẙhi ạllũjaju
 wakulũ tayãạri ạl̊gẖaḍab̊
 ạảm̊wāju ʿad̊liⁿ mur̊hibiⁿ
 wakā̊̉sa ḥuk̊minā sẖarib̊

[V4]
 4- wakulũ dẖā ḥas̊ba masẖīyảẗiⁿ
 waqaṣ̊diⁿ fī ạlạảzal̊
 wakulũ qaṣ̊di ạllhi bal̊
 tam̊jīduhu bihi ạk̊tamal̊

[V5]
 5- lidẖā masarãẗu ạl̊qadīr̊
 bihi waqal̊buhu ạr̊taḍay̱
 wahakadẖā rafãʿahu
 wafaẘqa kulĩ ạs̊miⁿ samā

[V6]
 6- lahu ạlsũjūdu wāltẖãnā
 wāl̊maj̊du wālsẖũk̊ru ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 lạảj̊li ḥubĩhi lanā
 wasaf̊ki damihi ạl̊karīm̊</lyrics>
<title>sr ạltqy̱ sr ʿẓym</title>
</song>